# List Pull Requests

Retrieve and filter pull requests for a repository or across repositories.

## gh CLI

```bash
# List open PRs (default)
gh pr list

# Filter by state
gh pr list --state closed
gh pr list --state merged
gh pr list --state all

# Filter by label, assignee, author
gh pr list --label bug --label urgent
gh pr list --assignee @me
gh pr list --author octocat

# Filter by base branch
gh pr list --base main
gh pr list --head feature/auth

# JSON output with specific fields
gh pr list --json number,title,state,author,createdAt --jq '.[] | "#\(.number) \(.title) by \(.author.login)"'

# Search across repos
gh search prs --repo owner/repo --state open --label bug
```

## REST API

```bash
# List open PRs
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $GITHUB_TOKEN" \
     "https://api.github.com/repos/owner/repo/pulls?state=open&sort=created&direction=desc&per_page=100"

# Filter by head and base
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $GITHUB_TOKEN" \
     "https://api.github.com/repos/owner/repo/pulls?head=owner:feature/auth&base=main"
```

```javascript
import { Octokit } from "@octokit/rest";
const octokit = new Octokit({ auth: process.env.GITHUB_TOKEN });

// List open PRs
const { data: prs } = await octokit.pulls.list({
  owner: "my-org",
  repo: "my-project",
  state: "open",
  sort: "created",
  direction: "desc",
  per_page: 100,
});

// Paginate all PRs
const allPRs = await octokit.paginate(octokit.pulls.list, {
  owner: "my-org",
  repo: "my-project",
  state: "all",
  per_page: 100,
});

// Search PRs across repos
const { data: results } = await octokit.search.issuesAndPullRequests({
  q: "repo:my-org/my-project is:pr is:open label:bug sort:updated-desc",
  per_page: 50,
});
console.log(`Found ${results.total_count} matching PRs`);
```

## GraphQL Query

```graphql
query($owner: String!, $name: String!, $cursor: String) {
  repository(owner: $owner, name: $name) {
    pullRequests(first: 50, after: $cursor, states: OPEN, orderBy: {field: CREATED_AT, direction: DESC}) {
      totalCount
      pageInfo { hasNextPage endCursor }
      nodes {
        number
        title
        state
        author { login }
        createdAt
        labels(first: 5) { nodes { name } }
        reviewDecision
        mergeable
      }
    }
  }
}
```

## Filter Parameters

| Parameter | Values | Description |
|-----------|--------|-------------|
| `state` | `open`, `closed`, `all` | PR state filter |
| `head` | `user:branch` | Filter by head branch |
| `base` | branch name | Filter by base branch |
| `sort` | `created`, `updated`, `popularity`, `long-running` | Sort field |
| `direction` | `asc`, `desc` | Sort direction |
